txt.en: Barricades can be found at Sutwarden in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy barricades at Sutwarden.
Barricades found at Sutwarden should be destroyed in order weaken the defences of your foes within the Wildwood.
Barricades can be found at Sutwarden in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy barricades at Sutwarden.
Foes of the Free Peoples have fortified the tower of Sutwarden within the Wildwood. Destroying the barricades here should weaken the Sutwarden defences.
